      "writtenOn": "2018-07-09T20:06:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "posix_memalign seems more limited than the previous scheme; one cannot allocate on alignments less than sizeof(void*), which means no 4 byte alignments, which in turn mean we can\u0027t match the default settings in OpenGL texture write/read",
      "parentUuid": "462e1fad_134b7e2f",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 101,
